title: Thiaoouba Prophecy - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/21/22
itunes:title: Thiaoouba Prophecy - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/21/22
description:
George Noory and translator Samuel Chong discuss his efforts to publish the story of Michel Desmarquet, a Frenchman who claimed he was abducted by eight foot tall aliens and taken to their advanced planet where he was given information about the universe.
